Create the Person Class

    Define attributes: Name, Gender, Address, Age.

    Create a constructor to initialize and print these attributes.

Create the Employee Class Extending Person

    Add attributes: Empid, Salary, Company_name, Qualification.

    Create a constructor to initialize and print these attributes, and call the Person constructor using super.

Create the Teacher Class Extending Employee

    Add attributes: Teacherid, Subject, Department.

    Create a constructor to initialize and print these attributes, and call the Employee constructor using super.

Implement the pgm8 Class with main Method

    Declare variables: name, gender, address, company_name, qualification, subject, department, age, empid, salary, teacherid.

    Use Scanner to read input values.

    Create a Teacher instance with the input values to invoke constructors and print details.
